\end_inset

 is a pair of a ground set 
\begin_inset Formula $E$
\end_inset

 (finite or infinite) and a set 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathcal{I}\subseteq2^{E}$
\end_inset

 satisfying the following independence axioms:
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
